## The Complete Flow Now

```
YOU (Postman)
    ↓
http://localhost:8080/api/items    ← single port
    ↓
API Gateway (8080)
    ↓ checks routing rules
    ↓ asks Eureka — where is item-service?
    ↓ Eureka says — 192.168.x.x:8081
    ↓
Item Service (8081)
    ↓ JWT check → Controller → Service → Repository → MySQL
    ↓
Response back to API Gateway
    ↓
Response back to YOU
```
